### TESTES PARA CLIENTES

### Buscar todos os clientes
GET http://localhost:40000/getAllClientes HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Buscar todos os clientes incluindo os com status inativo
GET http://localhost:40000/getAllClientesFilter HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Buscar cliente por ID
POST http://localhost:40000/getClienteByID HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "id_cliente": 2
}

